Typically written with the slash mark ⟨[[/]]⟩ and only spoken or transcribed as slash. Often omitted from speech and only marked as a brief pause between the alternatives. Exclusively omitted in common constructions such as {{term|and/or}}, {{term|either/or}}, and {{term|washer}}/{{term|dryer}}.

